  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You imbue your weapon with debilitating force lightning. As part of the action used to cast this power, you must make a melee weapon attack against one creature within your reach, otherwise the power fails. On a hit, the target suffers the attack's normal effects, and the lightning leaps from the target to a different creature of your choice that you can see within 5 feet of it. The second creature takes lightning damage equal to your forcecasting ability modifier.</p>\n<p>This power's damage increases when you reach higher levels. At 5th level, the melee attack deals an extra [[/r 1d8]] lightning damage to the target, and the lightning damage to the second creature increases to [[/r 1d8]] + your forcecasting ability modifier. Both damage rolls increase by [[/r 1d8]] at 11th level and 17th level.</p>",
